{"tid":2444312,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(Old News)《制服女生的觀察日記》用畫畫來詮釋瞬間記憶的功力","createTime":"2021-03-12T15:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T10:18:31.000Z","uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ded52eeebba0ca53c542ef25ec6f5553a4135b","tid":2444312,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">妄想力MAX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畫功MAX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n色氣度MAX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不知道螢幕前有多少人練習過速寫呢？這邊說得不是寫字快唷，而是指快速繪畫的一種方式，簡單說就是一種快速的素描，但僅僅勾勒出輪廓，形體，而不加繪肌理，光影之類的細節，透過大量練習獲得一定的經驗值後，我想大概就可以畫得跟今天的主題「制服女生的觀察日記」一樣了吧(我猜啦)<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVqA.jpg&h=f306d53f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今天這篇當中出現的圖，是來自日本繪師「壱河ふぇーす @rinc7600」的作品，他在2015年左右的時候，在網路上發表了不少「制服女生的觀察日記」，而最近這兩天又有人把這一系列的圖放到討論區聊一聊，有一些還沒看過的網友就表示，這根本就是妄想力開到極限的一種方式，敬佩有這種天份的同時，也有很多人佩服這位繪師，因為一瞬間看到的東西細節可以記的這麼清楚，這不是一件簡單的事情，而且又用畫畫來詮釋當時的影像記憶...太猛了<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVqg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVqg.jpg&h=cc1fbeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還有人覺得這畫風跟情境搭配的天衣無縫，讓人看了圖後非常的有感覺，雖然知道現實中被目擊到妹子可能不會這麼可愛，不果換個角度想想，當事人要是知道被畫成這麼可愛或許會很高興...<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVqw.jpg&h=b0a48fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只不過感到開心的同時，或許也會感到有點噁心吧！畢竟在那瞬間可是被觀察的相當仔細這樣(汗)<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVrA.jpg&h=ca8be9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關於畫面的呈現，這當中的細節仔細一看相當鉅細靡遺，不管是女孩的胸部、氣味甚至身體各部位都有相當的描寫<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVrQ.jpg&h=b630d8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n穿襯衫有沒有露出腋下、身上背的是什麼包包、甚至手上拿的書或是手機在上什麼網站，都被完整的記錄了下來<br />\n<br />\n完璧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完璧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完璧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完璧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完璧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVrg.jpg&h=f592822b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVrw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVrw.jpg&h=8929b300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVsA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVsA.jpg&h=ddf0fdb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CVqKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CVqKM.jpg&h=a2f042f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/69/82/pZ_Uoaaek6CWqKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F69%2F82%2FpZ_Uoaaek6CWqKQ.jpg&h=486ab957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1466982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1466982&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXIzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=581aad3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1466982</a>"},{"pid":"8bd6d10f41de0a93e3a3a3cf57367c1fb499151a","tid":2444312,"uid":251549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddc24e131f85089b217ac8adadb8ec2383282a1","tid":2444312,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac6ce34090e526032a302d900584246d515b4fc","tid":2444312,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"色氣唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}